Project Type: Category of the Project - Civil, Building, Park or Roadway
Site Storage: Is there site storage available for material?

Project Type: Categorical Variable - Type of project changes the cost allocations for hard costs and soft costs, as well as the amount spent on labor vs material, and the amount spent on heavy machinery or equipment
Site Storage: Categorical Variable - 0-No Storage/Deliver-and-Install; 1-Limited Storage/Small-Material, 2-Large Amount of Storage; Most NYC projects are "deliver and install" and have no site storage available; This binary flag captures that added logistical complexity. Larger projects that have heavy equipment or sitework, will normally have site storage available.
